about.summary: Functions for statistical analysis, prediction and control of time series based mainly on Akaike and Nakagawa (1988) <ISBN 978-90-277-2786-2>.

name: r-timsac
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '1.3.6' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-timsac
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/timsac_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/timsac/timsac_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 8fde280e3d2db81316990f3b9afeeba621624d80eb09deae9b432635710ac9a0

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 3
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}              # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_c') }}        # [win]
    - {{ compiler('fortran') }}        # [not win]
    - {{ compiler('m2w64_fortran') }}  # [win]
    - {{ posix }}filesystem        # [win]
    - {{ posix }}make
    - {{ posix }}sed               # [win]
    - {{ posix }}coreutils         # [win]
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
  run:
    - r-base
    - {{ native }}gcc-libs         # [win]

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('timsac')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('timsac')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=timsac
  license: GPL (>= 2)
  summary: Functions for statistical analysis, prediction and control of time series based mainly
    on Akaike and Nakagawa (1988) <ISBN 978-90-277-2786-2>.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - MathiasHaudgaard
    - FrodePedersen
    - ArneKr
